# directive-in-prefix-block

## Input

```
s {
#version 1
  k v
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..23
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..23
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    DIRECTIVE@4..14
      SHARP@4..5 "#"
      WORD@5..12 "version"
      LINE_STRING@12..14
        STRING@12..14 " 1"
    NEWLINE@14..15 "\n"
    SPACE@15..17 "  "
    ENTRY@17..21
      WORD_KEY@17..18
        WORD@17..18 "k"
      SPACE@18..19 " "
      LINE_STRING@19..20
        STRING@19..20 "v"
      NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@21..22 "}"
    NEWLINE@22..23 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                Directive {
                    sharp: SHARP@4..5 "#",
                    name: WORD@5..12 "version",
                    args: LineString {
                        string: STRING@12..14 " 1",
                    },
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@17..18 "k",
                    },
                    value: LineString {
                        string: STRING@19..20 "v",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@21..22 "}",
        },
    ],
}
